title: Flash Decompiler Trillix 3.0.3.470
description:
Flash Decompiler Trillix 3.0.3.470


Decompile SWF and convert to FLA
 
Convert SWF to FLA within seconds! Flash Decompiler Trillix is the only application capable of converting SWF to FLA with high speed, high quality and hundreds of additional features. Flash Decompiler Trillix is the ultimate tool to recover your lost FLA files - being the market leader since 2003! Decompile SWF files and obtain source code FLA in seconds. Moreover, since the Trillix version, meaning 3rd, Flash Decompiler supports batch conversion, so you can leave a bunch of different tasks to it and do any other things while Flash Decompiler is working.
